- disallow RTLD_GLOBAL flag for dlmopen in secondary namespaces (#197462)
- PI mutex support

* 一 7月 10 2006 Jakub Jelinek <jakub@redhat.com> 2.4.90-13
- DT_GNU_HASH support

* 五 6月 30 2006 Jakub Jelinek <jakub@redhat.com> 2.4.90-12
