  x86_64

* 四 5月 20 2004 Jakub Jelinek <jakub@redhat.com> 2.3.3-29
- use lib64 instead of lib on ia64 if %{_lib} is defined to lib64

* 三 5月 19 2004 Jakub Jelinek <jakub@redhat.com> 2.3.3-28
