* 二 5月 04 2004 Jakub Jelinek <jakub@redhat.com> 2.3.3-24
- update from CVS
  - define S_ISSOCK in -D_XOPEN_SOURCE=600 and S_I[FS]SOCK
    plus F_[SG]ETOWN also in -D_XOPEN_SOURCE=500 (both
    included already in XNS5)
